{"type": "article", "id": 9081, "title": "迷你工具笔", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-01T08:38:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 12, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235144LTjFfrS1pP5IWouH.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t台北设计工作室 Mininch 最近推出了一款迷你工具笔，它们的“笔芯”是一字刀、十字刀、六角刀等不同款式的螺丝刀头，使用时只需要更换刀头，就可以满足不同环境下的使用要求。表面材料采用的是轻质碳素钢材，设计简单干净，便于携带。颜色上有香槟色，银色，青铜色可以选择。目前正在Kickstarter 上众筹，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/2054052511/tool-pen-mini-precision-bits\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235141uCltKk1AcBVfJ2TP.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.62571429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235142ipsWY6jVzTRUFwu4.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235142XPeMz3bAE4xDn8ah.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.65665236\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235142r9SlahHsPZy01D7v.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.62571429\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235143eCPU5if3nLSvNV7T.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.68714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}